FBIS4-61601 "drsov089_r_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-089 Daily Report 8 May 1994 Azerbaijan Azeri Troops Resume Offensive on Mardakert Region Azeri Troops Resume Offensive on Mardakert Region LD0805170694 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1614 GMT 8 May 94 LD0805170694 Moscow INTERFAX English BFN [Text] Sunday morning the Azeri troops resumed their offensive in the direction of the villages of Chailu and Leninavan in the north of Mardakert Region of Nagorny Karabakh [Nagorno-Karabakh]. They are supported by artillery and armored vehicles. Military actions are continuing all along the front line, said the press service of Nagorny Karabakh's defence army. According to reports issued at 1200 on Sunday, the Karabakh forces have repulsed all attacks. Their enemy sustained losses in personnel and military equipment. Concrete losses are not known yet. At the other sectors of the front routine exchanges of fire went on last night and Sunday morning.
